          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-262-0852-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">A</hi> BARD on whom <hi rend="italics">Phœbus</hi> his Spirit bestow'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-0852-line-2" n="2">Resolving t'acknowledge the Bounty he ow'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-0852-line-3" n="3">Found out a new Method at once of confessing,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-0852-line-4" n="4">And making the most of so mighty a Blessing;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-0852-line-5" n="5">To the God he'd be grateful, but Mortals he'd chouse,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-0852-line-6" n="6">By making his Patron preside in his House,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-0852-line-7" n="7">And wisely foresaw his Advantage from thence,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-0852-line-8" n="8">That the God wou'd in Honour bear most of th' Expence:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-0852-line-9" n="9">So, the Bard he finds Drink, and leaves <hi rend="italics">Phœbus</hi> to treat</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-0852-line-10" n="10">With the Thoughts he inspires, regardless of Meat.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-0852-line-11" n="11">Hence they that come hither expecting to dine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-0852-line-12" n="12">Are always fobb'd off with sheer Wit and sheer Wine.</l>
          </lg>
